<p>Hello <%= @resource.name %>,</p>

<p><%= @resource.invited_by.present? ? @resource.invited_by.name : 'Someone' %> has invited you to fill out your <%= ENV['TOURNEY_NAME'] %> bracket at <%= link_to 'Pool Madness', root_url %>. You can accept it through the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Accept invitation', accept_invitation_url(@resource, :invitation_token => @resource.invitation_token) %></p>

<p>If you don't want to accept the invitation, please ignore this email.<br />
  Your account won't be created until you access the link above and set your password.</p>

<p>All entries are $10 and must be paid by this Thursday at Noon Eastern.</p>

<p>Just a reminder, after you accept the invitation you can login in with your email address and password at
  <%= link_to root_url, root_url %>.
</p>

<p>Good Luck!</p>

